<div class="title">Truth Serum</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DT&Exact=1">DT</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DT. "Truth Serum: An Experience with Alcohol (exp64279)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 29, 2009. erowid.org/exp/64279</div>

<br/>



